text: Elizabeth Street Mall Elizabeth Street Mall is a pedestrian street mall in Hobart, Tasmania. It is located on Elizabeth Street between Collins Street and Liverpool Street. It is the largest shopping area in the Hobart city centre. It is also a busy meeting place and busking area. ==References== Category:Pedestrian malls in Australia Category:Shopping districts and streets in Australia Category:Streets in Hobart Category:Tourist attractions in Hobart
